Titolo: Revelation Online

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Revelation Online is a free-to-play massive multiplayer online role-playing game developed by NetEase, under the title "Revelation" (Chinese: 天谕; pinyin: Tiān Yù) in China and Revelation Online in the rest of the world. It is published by My.com in Europe and North America, and received an open release worldwide on March 6, 2017. The game features classic MMORPG gameplay and is set in a world inspired by the books of the Chinese fantasy author Jiang Nan. Revelation Online receives regular update content updates, with the latest, Heaven and Earth, due for release in 2019.

Genere: MMORPG

Valutazione: N/A
